content:
The Ukrainian heavy UAV Vampire, which the Russians are called "grandmother Yaga", arranges a real hell in the positions of the invaders.

Video of night work dronesIt has releasedThe North Operational Command, reports the Armyinform.

"Our Baba Yaga loves raids at night at the positions of the Russian military and fry those who came to our land with weapons," the statement said.

Earlier the Armyinformreportedthat Ukrainian Achilles destroyed 5 units of armored vehicles.
title: Baba Yaga again fry a dozen occupiers
description: Video of the night work of drones was released by the operational command "North", reports ...
author: Army Inform
